.TH "snd_pcm_lib_default_mmap" 9 "snd_pcm_lib_default_mmap" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_pcm_lib_default_mmap \- Default PCM data mmap function
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" snd_pcm_lib_default_mmap
.BI "(struct snd_pcm_substream *substream "  ","
.BI "struct vm_area_struct *area "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "substream" 12
PCM substream
.IP "area" 12
VMA
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This is the default mmap handler for PCM data.  When mmap pcm_ops is NULL,
this function is invoked implicitly.
